{"tid":2387634,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Steam Game - The Day Before ﹝開放世界大型喪屍生存遊戲﹞","createTime":"2021-01-30T12:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T15:28:43.000Z","uid":59152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"772531b1bb305c585afa8422bf1fb3a28cbb7b36","tid":2387634,"uid":59152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T12:56:51.000Z","msg":"《The Day Before》由 Fnatastic 開發，係一款開放世界多人大型線上生存遊戲，採用第三身視點。遊戲舞台位於美國近紐約地區，因為病毒大流行爆發，感染者變得渴求人肉，倖存者亦互相殘殺爭奪物資，而我地所扮演嘅角色因為喺病毒爆發前一晚處於昏迷狀態避過一劫，醒來之後發現已經唔係佢所熟悉嘅世界，為咗生存決定同其他玩家合作或者合力廝殺。<br />\n<br />\n會唔會有人一齊玩 似正!!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/46493/new-open-world-mmo-survival-the-day-before-announcement?fbclid=IwAR1Rwbgl-TxwoK1LvxI8akTVEfNTHkbmQXWeBKVg--FdHA4PcNTf04kMdks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F46493%2Fnew-open-world-mmo-survival-the-day-before-announcement%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Rwbgl-TxwoK1LvxI8akTVEfNTHkbmQXWeBKVg--FdHA4PcNTf04kMdks&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=acb88d34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/46493/new-open-world-mmo-survival-the-day-before-announcement?fbclid=IwAR1Rwbgl-TxwoK1LvxI8akTVEfNTHkbmQXWeBKVg--FdHA4PcNTf04kMdks</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.price.com.hk/news.php?id=16206&amp;sec_id=14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fnews.php%3Fid%3D16206%26sec_id%3D14&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=a31093ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.price.com.hk/news.php?id=16206&amp;sec_id=14</a>"},{"pid":"39464b01cc43306d25b1648df52850a202ecb3c6","tid":2387634,"uid":158598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"睇定D先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d69e354459c1c35722ebbc9559b43d29d78585","tid":2387634,"uid":59152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13